underlying_goal: To commit recent slide clarification changes to the git repository.
primary_success: Accurately summarized a set of slide improvements and created a single, well-messaged git commit, while correctly ignoring the untracked exported PDF.
brief_summary: Following a user command to commit, Claude analyzed the changes to the Week 19 slides, summarizing them as clarity and formatting improvements. It created a single logical commit with a clear message and correctly ignored the accompanying generated PDF file. The commit workflow was completed successfully.
